{"tid":10753,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"想問下各位巴打用飛機杯戴唔戴套？","createTime":"2016-11-29T05:17:54.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T05:44:06.000Z","uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2dcae846178c83299f9f487371ed19a8325874fd","tid":10753,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:17:54.000Z","msg":"前排就買左個飛機杯比佢啦<br />\n咁我就唔知佢有無用過<br />\n但我岩岩睇櫃桶發覺少左個condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問佢點解<br />\n佢話無 <br />\nChok多兩chok就話拎左黎打飛機費是洗個杯<br />\n<br />\n想問下各位巴打會唔會戴套打飛機？<br />\n依家個心好亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc68c0734029a1a40415cb7fd92ac638956ee408","tid":10753,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:18:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86e65c253b0b22545e739af2e6e3d0a7abb3e259","tid":10753,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:19:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa999b32acc18e35e2457c726fde093e41db551e","tid":10753,"uid":36278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:19:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你自己平時有無用開套打飛機"},{"pid":"d3675d5341129a36df8455140946a5c492662db3","tid":10753,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:20:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你自己平時有無用開套打飛機</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n。。。女人點打飛機。。。"},{"pid":"181ea1a2c441bfbca19832c87af839e78521d984","tid":10753,"uid":36392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:23:59.000Z","msg":"唔好諗咁多，唔想洗杯呢個理由好合理，佢有心唔俾你知出街買都得啦。"},{"pid":"88cbbac4fc93125a403ba4b64998e04585ed60e1","tid":10753,"uid":18241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:24:11.000Z","msg":"戴套打飛機=雙層魚柳包"},{"pid":"c93fe092de218d2f12220b51e91f4cf97142c2d6","tid":10753,"uid":6310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:24:18.000Z","msg":"唔會，但屌第二條女就會"},{"pid":"fb6530d716b595b731e07361a632d80e161b2286","tid":10753,"uid":20652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:25:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff433c4af947a0de5f8cf2e54902569adb62e585","tid":10753,"uid":660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:25:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你自己平時有無用開套打飛機</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n。。。女人點打飛機。。。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n女人可以幫男人打飛機架姐<br />\n你連呢個都唔知仲想扮女人？"},{"pid":"24c989abba4380038f58af42e87f5842a632d8ec","tid":10753,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:27:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你自己平時有無用開套打飛機</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n。。。女人點打飛機。。。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n女人可以幫男人打飛機架姐<br />\n你連呢個都唔知仲想扮女人？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未試過幫佢用飛機杯打飛機。。。"},{"pid":"23b44d32c887332d0678a0ad519996d1957c1779","tid":10753,"uid":10025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:29:53.000Z","msg":"有兩條女仲駛乜用飛機杯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6962d4b5f0d2662771f627630e4912d3baaa0164","tid":10753,"uid":23339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:31:02.000Z","msg":"是咁的，<br />\n飛機杯戴套我覺得好正常。<br />\n<br />\n原因好簡單，香港地，物價貴，飛機杯仲貴。<br />\n屈臣氏宜家緊緻深喉就賣緊200蚊<br />\n（打飛機冇理由要用Cheap嘢）<br />\n學生哥幾條友辛辛苦苦夾到個200蚊買到個飛機杯冇可能淨係畀一條友霸住使<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以你再夾多80幾蚊買三個0.02杜蕾斯condom，<br />\n三條友share用個飛機杯，其實係好抵。<br />\n<br />\nTenga飛機杯係一次性；<br />\n但戴condom打飛機用嘅condom，<br />\n只要冇穿到，就可以好輕易咁清洗，循環再用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n窮撚三條，每人用1舊水唔使就可以成就夢想，<br />\n何樂而不為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n<br />\n(雖然日本貴啲嘅都係一個含稅750円)<br />\n<br />\nPS：以前次次去完日本返嚟，一定會帶啲飛機杯返嚟益街坊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但宜家香港有Tenga嘅銷售代理商，我諗緊我係咪應該考慮轉買電動假陽具返嚟益下啲絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/29/132924_2f54c320c6eabb0d01528474b08c6db7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F29%2F132924_2f54c320c6eabb0d01528474b08c6db7.jpg&h=b0a4a846&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/02d375k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F02d375k.jpg&h=60997253&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/187L75P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F187L75P.jpg&h=395194e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc6d5f429c052bd4f8a77e90d3613af78f70b661","tid":10753,"uid":23339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:35:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是咁的，<br />\n飛機杯戴套我覺得好正常。<br />\n<br />\n原因好簡單，香港地，物價貴，飛機杯仲貴。<br />\n屈臣氏宜家緊緻深喉就賣緊200蚊<br />\n（打飛機冇理由要用Cheap嘢）<br />\n學生哥幾條友辛辛苦苦夾到個200蚊買到個飛機杯冇可能淨係畀一條友霸住使<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以你再夾多80幾蚊買三個0.02杜蕾斯condom，<br />\n三條友share用個飛機杯，其實係好抵。<br />\n<br />\nTenga飛機杯係一次性；<br />\n但戴condom打飛機用嘅condom，<br />\n只要冇穿到，就可以好輕易咁清洗，循環再用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n窮撚三條，每人用1舊水唔使就可以成就無數次夢想，<br />\n何樂而不為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n<br />\n(雖然日本貴啲嘅都係一個含稅750円)<br />\n<br />\nPS：以前次次去完日本返嚟，一定會帶啲飛機杯返嚟益街坊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但宜家香港有Tenga嘅銷售代理商，我諗緊我係咪應該考慮轉買電動假陽具返嚟益下啲絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/29/132924_2f54c320c6eabb0d01528474b08c6db7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F29%2F132924_2f54c320c6eabb0d01528474b08c6db7.jpg&h=c28a8e21&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://na.cx/i/02d375k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F02d375k.jpg&h=eea14656&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://na.cx/i/187L75P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F187L75P.jpg&h=b769a0e4&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\noff tpoic 自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb3a0e7802cb097ed3e4b9fbdcced14bc783ab3c","tid":10753,"uid":29439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:36:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是咁的，<br />\n飛機杯戴套我覺得好正常。<br />\n<br />\n原因好簡單，香港地，物價貴，飛機杯仲貴。<br />\n屈臣氏宜家緊緻深喉就賣緊200蚊<br />\n（打飛機冇理由要用Cheap嘢）<br />\n學生哥幾條友辛辛苦苦夾到個200蚊買到個飛機杯冇可能淨係畀一條友霸住使<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以你再夾多80幾蚊買三個0.02杜蕾斯condom，<br />\n三條友share用個飛機杯，其實係好抵。<br />\n<br />\nTenga飛機杯係一次性；<br />\n但戴condom打飛機用嘅condom，<br />\n只要冇穿到，就可以好輕易咁清洗，循環再用